#: data/io.github.ikajdan.steammetadatatool.desktop:7
#: data/io.github.ikajdan.steammetadatatool.metainfo.xml:10
msgid "A tool for managing Steam client game metadata and library artwork"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.ikajdan.steammetadatatool.metainfo.xml:12
msgid ""
"SteamMetadataTool is a desktop utility for inspecting and customizing the "
"game metadata used by the Steam client. It reads the local appinfo.vdf "
"database, shows installed app records in a searchable interface, and allows "
"users to apply custom metadata overrides and artwork to their Steam library."
msgstr ""

